                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I was sent for, and took her and the waistroat.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went into the shop to look at the blouses, and rolled my little girl's shawl up in my apron; I put it on the counter, and said I would call again in a few minutes.; when I got about fifty yards from the door he came, took me back, searched me, and found no waistcoat; I had been in the shop half an hour when the servant found the waistcoat.</p>
